Description: Europris ASA is a Norway-based discount retailer. The Company offers its customers a broad range of private-label and brand-name merchandise across 15 product categories: Personal care, Groceries, Laundry and cleaning, Clothes and shoes, Hobby and office, Handyman, Travel, sport and leisure, Electronics, Chocolate and snacks, Pet food and accessories, Carpet and home textiles, Kitchen, House and garden, Candles and interior, and Storage.
